  @positive
  Scenario Outline: TotalRecords is set to <totalRecords>
    When I set totalRecords to "<totalRecords>"
      And I check paginate checkbox
    Then totalRecords is set to "<totalRecords>" records
    Examples:
      | totalRecords |
      | 0            |
      | 10           |
      | 100          |
      | 99999999     |
      | -1           |
      | -10          |

  @positive
